Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:08.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GDF Base on the Front Lines\N"Undina" Air Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<"The primitive beings!\NHunt them down to the last one!">
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The UOA and EEU armies have evacuated!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We've lost contact with the Third Asteroid Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firewalls for Bases 1 through 3 have collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Wulgaru ship is approaching\Nthe transmission satellite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transmission satellite destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Smith, please head to the\NCommand Room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Undina Base is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The UPI Army should fall back like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they break through...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should protect Undina with our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As things currently stand,\Nwe cannot defend the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want everyone to die in vain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your decision please, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will retreat. The UPI Army\Nwill abandon Undina Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence the evacuation plan immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please provide fresh soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Commander Simon\Nfrom the secret service, MJP.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MJP...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majestic Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.39,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sortie"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence mock battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tamaki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's draw in closer before\Nwe commence the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 1 has been shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto for Unit 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Unit 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dyin' to shoot those punks down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have received the worst scores\Nyet again, Team Rabbits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from the Fail Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we got the worst score.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you shouldn't have tried\Nto be a big shot and charged ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thought of attacking as a team\Nhad totally flown out of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one to talk, you wannabe sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you load live ammo onto a practice unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live ammo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a newb could see that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're practice shells based on their blue coat job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be a student here\Nand not know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kn-knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you are aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you have the lowest grades\Nyet again this semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you are by any means incompetent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you fall apart in team battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are fumbling over each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please change my team.\NI cannot fight with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Submit a report analyzing the reasoning and basis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for why you cannot fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dragging us down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Fail Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call us that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SALTED SQUID GUTS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got turned down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he did was treat you kindly once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's still way popular amongst gun enthusiasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Its velvety texture is just like your skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And this slide-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to put your tray up\Nwhen you finish eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suruga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up on your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme is "Love and Justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen? I mean, if Undina falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be pretty bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the enemy really looks like aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. They haven't been able to\Nconfirm even that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably won't be sent hunting\Nfor a good while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my love will bear fruit first...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your bosom the only thing growing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. I'm sure it'll work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When'll that be?! Is it soon or a long ways off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lame attempt to comfort her\Nwill have the opposite effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You totally don't get how a girl's heart works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor Suzukaze, Commander Simon\Nwould like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have received a sortie request from GDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are participating in the\NUndina Evacuation Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather Team Rabbits together and have\Nthem prepare to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't ready for this yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Rabbits, report to Gate 0131 ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate 0131? Doesn't that gate\Nlead to outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Are they gonna exile us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was in the groove...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:07:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, could I have that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Respect what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was lost on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru, you're also a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, there are five units...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Rabbits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Rabbits will hereby depart for Undina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, isn't Undina currently\Nunder Wulgaru attack...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be briefed about your mission\Nupon boarding Godinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Transport the AHSMB units into the Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I repeat: Transport the AHSMB into the Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, this would be our first time\Npiloting actual units...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their basic commands are\Nthe same as the practice units.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they should prove easier to pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The JURIA-SYSTEM\Nhas been uploaded into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Juria again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By incorporating the pilot's DNA,\Nthis system increases AHSMB's precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have already uploaded your DNA data\Ninto the JURIA-SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I shall announce your formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunner: Suruga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control Unit: Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booster Unit: Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward Unit: Asagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the leader... is Izuru Hitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be the leader in this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Godinion.\NRequesting permission for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is control.\NGodinion is cleared for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleared for takeoff. All ranges: Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Increasing backup engine output.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NActivating turbine activation sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,External power has been established.\NDisconnect all equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}AUP activated.\NAll hatches closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,External pressure increasing. Turbines activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Main engine military!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undina is the GDF's frontline base,\Nlocated at coordinates CR-34.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is currently under enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe are to evacuate and abandon this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must buy time while the personnel\Nevacuate Undina Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will finish evacuating in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We expect the base to fall in 2.5 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is throw the enemy into disarray and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,upset their plans for thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't respond without thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how hard this is gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to pull this off...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the sigh of relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, this is the first time\Nno one snapped at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our leader...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we want to nitpick over the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you heard, Undina Base is in a dire situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can still change the tide of war if we swiftly evacuate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as many people as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your dreams at present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream has already come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my dream to fight piloting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a cutting-edge unit as a member of the GDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess that goes for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never put any thought into what my dream is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-my dweam ish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the GDF's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall hereby commence Operation Sarvar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, prepare for sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forward unit dogfights in the vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a versatile midrange battle unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's set to prioritize bursts of\Nnear-instant acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on the throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The control unit uses a\Nwide-range battle alert system,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will be your eyes and ears\Non the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A single order from your control unit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can determine whether your team lives or dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shocked by the boosters' speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This puppy can fly faster than\Na high-speed planetary cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Constantly move as you\Nthrow the enemy into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gunner uses...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long-ranged attacks with a\Nhigh-energy charged particle cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and radiation-guided photon resonance\Nantiaircraft artillery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you're knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a full-power volley, the time lag
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and acceleration will be a beat off, so watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your unit is meant for the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the forward unit, it is versatile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is capable of handling even\Nhigher-level command transmissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep constant tab on all incoming information on each unit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and issue the appropriate commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done with the explanations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bunnies, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be deploying in the Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us know if you need any weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe'll send them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also let us know if you need any\Nemergency maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, AHSMB break easily in exchange\Nfor their high-energy output.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We've got your backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Godinion, enter Combat Formation I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Main control: Move CIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navi bridge: Closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulkhead: Locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whole control room: Move complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You connected with your AHSMB.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We connected...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are linked together with your AHSMB.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That activates the JURIA-SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready for standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All vessels enter detachment mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detachment mode: Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the bolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pits, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignite thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All vessels are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All vessels, activate thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Pit vessels have reached\Ntheir designated positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verification checks are complete.\NOutput is increasing normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All AHSMB units have taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<"Don't let them escape! Crush them all!">
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, they'll kill everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying aircrafts not in the codebook\Nare approaching from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is a GDF code...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The MJP?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we've come to quite the hot spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think we'll make it back alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am John Smith, Operations Commander\Nat GDF Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lt. Commander Suzukaze of the MJP.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Commander Suzukaze, please have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,units 1-5 commence battle at Secret Code Delta Zulu-41.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Commence battle at Delta Zulu-41.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All AHSMB units have turned\Non the emergency brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Get into your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What?! Now it's moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AHSMB has a mind of its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your survival instinct is moving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you decide to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the JURIA-SYSTEM's\Ndefensive instincts will remain active.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defensive instincts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't fight, we'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The AHSMB units have reached their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is split into three waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First attack the one in the 2 o'clock direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this acceleration?!\N It's too sensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose 3, activate your shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red 5, Blue 1, activate your shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Retreat while they're buying us some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose 3, launch your missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undina Base's Third Mobile Infantry Regiment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Outer Planetary Army's\N21st Regiment have finished evacuating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evacuation is complete.\N Return promptly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are still down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Purple 2. Godinion, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GDF Headquarters, there are still people\Nin the Civilian Residential District.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But-!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any ships left for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Units 1-5, return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are still down there.\NAnd there are so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any ships left for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it our mission to make sure\Nthat everyone escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Several enemy ships are approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there aren't any vessels,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only way to save those
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people is to defeat all of the enemy ships here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we pull that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't become a hero\Nif you don't do the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't match you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you actin' so fired up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you serious about becoming a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we're stuck fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you retreating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously intend to face\Nthe enemy's main fleet head on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no choice but to fight now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we win this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really should be running.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away? Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away. Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<"Destroy that red one!">
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red 5, you're over-exerting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru, to your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it move on its own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEP Cannon: Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire at maximum power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red 5 is fully storming the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<"Lord Rada, we won't be able to escape if we stay">
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<"Enough! I grow weary of this battle. This hunt is over">
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy fleet has retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming that all AHSMB units are intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.84,0:22:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy fleet is pulling away from Undina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThey are headed toward Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They protected a base\Nthat we were going to abandon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:56.04,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Heroes are Born"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:57.24,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,
